## Platform Architecture ğŸ—ï¸
- **Flask**: Lightweight Python web framework for creating the API ğŸŒ  
- **SQLAlchemy**: ORM for managing and accessing the database ğŸ—„ï¸  
- **SQLite**: A simple and effective local database ğŸ› ï¸  

